      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration experts! This vehicle is the ultimate project opportunity for someone looking to build their dream car from the ground up. While it is currently in poor condition and needs a total overhaul to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation for a dedicated hobbyist. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge and a way to customize a vehicle to your exact specifications, this is the one for you!",
