      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, a specimen that exemplifies automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains devoid of wear. Mechanically superior and cosmetically flawless, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a benchmark-quality asset. Its condition is absolute, representing the pinnacle of its class.",
